{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji28.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给周起鹦的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给周起鹦的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年5月16日）起先生："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年十月来信收到，甚为感谢。菊年现名周文楠²，在沈阳人民法院工作。先生仍以在现地工作为好，虽不适意，犹胜于失职（业）者，尚希安心从事，然后徐图改进。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此复，即祝康吉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五○年五月十六日[1]周起鹗，周文楠的侄子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[2]周文楠，原是毛泽东之弟毛泽覃的夫人。当时任沈阳市人民法院刑事庭庭长。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":5,"day":16}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":403,"page_end":403},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}